The currently available simplegeo .Net client library referenced at simplegeo.com seems somewhat.. orphan and outdated and even though I'd like to contribute, VisualBasic.Net is a personal show-stopper for me.

That's why I decided to hack away a C# / .Net 4 based client library.

Enjoy!

